  AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM "Question" q2 WHERE q2."examId" = e.id AND q2.stem = $patch$A Python developer needs to send a REST API call to modify a specific field of an existing resource on a Cisco DNA Center controller without replacing the entire resource. Which HTTP method should the developer use?$patch$);
